					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can't even use any of the single-bit latches without support circuitry anyway. So if you're going to use a discrete logic mapper you may as well use a 74'161 or 74'377 to get <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/User:Lidnariq/Discrete_Logic_Table" class="postlink">a bit more space</a>.</div>

